OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fmostly dry this evening. Showers will
OL,7,Fgradually fade away into tonight;
OL,8,Fhowever, some may linger in the west.
OL,9,FRemaining largely cloudy and generally
OL,10,Fmild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FCloudy for many on bank
OL,13,Fholiday Monday but mostly dry with
OL,14,Fjust the odd shower. Perhaps a few
OL,15,Fbright spells emerging. Temperatures
OL,16,Fclose to normal for early May.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
